				\begin{document}$$^{10}$$\end{document}10 (100 dB) on the few 10 ps scale. Fig. 8 depicts a typical contrast optimized double-CPA laser system, using the principle example of the Draco laser system. Ultrashort pulses are generated by a mode-locked oscillator yielding low pulse energy (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
